ingredientsDesc:
VITROS Rubella IgM Reagent Pack (1484427) contains：
-100 coated wells (streptavidin source, binding capacity≥3 ng biotin/well).
-18.0 mL biotinylated antibody reagent﹝biotin-mouse monoclonal anti-human IgM, 0.75 μg/mL﹞in buffer with antimicrobial agent.
-13.1 mL conjugate reagent﹝HRP-mouse monoclonal IgG anti-rubella 34 ng/mL; UV treated rubella antigen 1.2 μg/mL﹞in buffer with antimicrobial agent.
VITROS Rubella IgM Calibrators (8017600) contains：
- 1 VITROS Rubella IgM calibrator (0.85 mL human rubella IgM positive plasma) with antimicrobial agent.
